#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "The OTRS stats module holds features to track operational statistics and "
#| "generate custom reports associated with OTRS usage. The OTRS system uses "
#| "the term \"stat\" generically to refer to a report presenting various "
#| "indicators."
msgid ""
"The OTRS stats module holds features to track operational statistics and "
"generates custom reports associated with OTRS usage. The OTRS system uses "
"the term \"stat\" generically to refer to a report presenting various "
"indicators."
msgstr ""
"Das OTRS-Statistikmodul enthält Funktionen, um betriebliche Kennziffern zu "
"überwachen und angepasste Reports der Verwendung von OTRS zu erstellen. In "
