#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/source.xml:33
msgid "<emphasis>Script: First steps to install OTRS.</emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Skript: Erste Schritte bei der Installation von OTRS.</emphasis>"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/source.xml:37
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "OTRS should NOT be run with root rights. You should add a new user for "
#| "OTRS as the next step. The home directory of this new user should be "
#| "<filename>/opt/otrs</filename>. If your web server is not running with "
#| "the same user rights as the new 'otrs' user, which is the case on most "
#| "systems, you have to add the new 'otrs' user to the group of the web "
#| "server user (see Script below)."
msgid ""
"OTRS should NOT be run with root rights. Next you should add a new user for "
"OTRS. The home directory of this new user should be <filename>/opt/otrs</"
"filename>. If your web server is not running with the same user rights as "
"the new 'otrs' user, which is the case on most systems, you will need to add "
"the new 'otrs' user to the group of the web server user (see Script below)."
msgstr ""
"Da die Skripte von OTRS später nicht mit root-Rechten laufen sollen, muss im "
"nächsten Schritt ein Benutzer für OTRS im System angelegt werden. Dieser "
"Benutzer sollte als Homeverzeichnis das Verzeichnis erhalten, in das gerade "
"die Quellen von OTRS entpackt wurden, also<filename>/opt/otrs</filename>. "
"Wird der Webserver unter einem anderen Benutzer als dem OTRS-User betrieben, "
"so muss der neue OTRS-Benutzer noch zur Gruppe des Webserver-Users "
"hinzugefügt werden."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/installation/source.xml:43
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"linux:/opt# useradd -r -d /opt/otrs/ -c 'OTRS user' otrs\n"
"linux:/opt# usermod -G nogroup otrs\n"
"linux:/opt#\n"
msgstr ""
"linux:/opt# useradd -r -d /opt/otrs/ -c 'OTRS user' otrs\n"
"linux:/opt# usermod -G nogroup otrs\n"
"linux:/opt#\n"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/source.xml:50
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Script: Adding a new user 'otrs', and adding it to a group.</"
"emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Skript: Anlegen eines neuen Nutzers 'otrs' und Hinzufügung zu "
"desselben zu einer Gruppe.</emphasis>"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/installation/source.xml:54
msgid ""
"Next, you have to copy some sample configuration files. The system will "
"later use the copied files. The files are located in <filename>/opt/otrs/"
"Kernel</filename> and <filename>/opt/otrs/Kernel/Config</filename> and have "
"the suffix .dist (see Script below)."
msgstr ""
"Im nächsten Schritt werden einige Demo-Konfigurationsdateien innerhalb der "
"entpackten Quelldateien bzw. innerhalb des Homeverzeichnisses des OTRS-"
"Benutzers kopiert. Die Dateien befinden sich in den Verzeichnissen "
"<filename>/opt/otrs/Kernel</filename> bzw. <filename>/opt/otrs/Kernel/"
"Config</filename> und haben die Endung .dist."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para><screen>
#: en/content/installation/source.xml:59
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"linux:/opt# cd otrs/Kernel/\n"
"linux:/opt/otrs/Kernel# cp Config.pm.dist Config.pm\n"
"linux:/opt/otrs/Kernel# cd Config\n"
"linux:/opt/otrs/Kernel/Config# cp GenericAgent.pm.dist GenericAgent.pm\n"
